Reader adapter which limits the bytes read from an underlying reader.

This struct is generally created by calling [`take`](about:blank/trait.Read.html#method.take "method std::io::Read::take") on a reader. Please see the documentation of [`take`](about:blank/trait.Read.html#method.take "method std::io::Read::take") for more details.

